---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets'
import boneRadio from '../assets/bone-radio.png'
import SectionTitleLayout from '../layouts/SectionTitleLayout.astro'
---

<section id="context" class="py-16 sm:py-20">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
    <SectionTitleLayout
      title="The Challenge in Bone Repair"
      subtitle="Understanding the critical issues in current bone repair methods"
    />
    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-12">
      <div class="lg:flex lg:flex-col lg:justify-between lg:w-1/2">
        <div class="sm:bg-lightGray sm:rounded-xl sm:p-8">
          <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Bone fractures are very common traumas. Today, <strong
              >10% of bone defects don't repair</strong
            >, and it can reach <strong>45% for risk patients</strong> (diabetes,
            elderly, osteoporosis, smokers).
          </p>
          <p class="leading-relaxed">
            In the case of severe trauma, the standard solution is autograft but
            the amount of available bone is limited, and the surgical procedure
            is painful for the patient.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-6 grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="bg-primary/10 rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
            <span class="text-3xl font-bold">10%</span>
            <p class="text-sm mt-2">Defects don't repair</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-primary/10 rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
            <span class="text-3xl font-bold">45%</span>
            <p class="text-sm mt-2">Risk patients</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex-grow">
        <div class="relative">
          <Image
            src={boneRadio}
            alt="Bone fracture illustration"
            class="md:hidden relative rounded-2xl shadow-lg w-full object-cover aspect-4/3"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="sync"
          />
          <Image
            src={boneRadio}
            alt="Bone fracture illustration"
            class="hidden md:block relative rounded-2xl shadow-lg w-full object-cover aspect-4/3"
            loading="eager"
            decoding="sync"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
